This error also applies when you wrap any widget with an `OutlineInputBorder()` in a SizeTransition.

This clips the floating label.

The widget should expand it's size to contain the floating label.


With `SizeTransition`

<img width="804" height="402" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/927efdf8-5203-4591-b57f-256a7415f00b" />

Without SizeTransition

